author: COMSOL
description: This example computes the impedance of a capacitor with an applied sinusoidally time-varying voltage difference over a wide frequency range. The relationship between the frequency-domain impedance and the steady-state capacitance and resistance of the device is discussed and solver accuracy is addressed.
